></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXTRA MATERIAL</h2>Exclusive to this compilation is the supplemental material called <i>Please Read</i>, which contains :<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>More than 20 documents to unlock that explore the narrative of the Please universe in more details<br></li><li>A new secret ending, revealing the actual events of the official timeline<br></li><li>Quality Of Life improvements and bug fixes</li></ul>",
